{"tid":1291808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呀sir,我要報警","createTime":"2019-07-07T04:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T06:40:43.000Z","uid":140326,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9ae287ab0c2de0a936c74b4a1119fe05c19cef","tid":1291808,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"遊行其間有人出現打人點算？<br />\n首先要盡量拍片做證據<br />\n再捉住佢唔比佢走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在鏡頭面前針對【一個】警察，望下佢膊頭number, 大大聲講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「警察編號PC3456」我而家要報警</span></span>，我有拍片<br />\n<br />\n要有心理準備佢地未必會拉人，<br />\n呢個時候對住另一個警察講同樣說話<br />\n目的要針對個別警員，要佢地知道唔做野就會上身，<br />\n同埋之後放上網做文宣<br />\n<br />\n捉一個打人廢物，同用呢啲黑材料做文宣，<br />\n你話邊個有殺傷力啲"},{"pid":"df854bf2c22fb2ce42a6fce62f0d24b83baebdd2","tid":1291808,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbbe77710cf2abf6d9669ed64bcae9c78eb8c5a3","tid":1291808,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:16:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e220f11cf32db86f86dc7fd89222b175fb7bb154","tid":1291808,"uid":99402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"有number先得嫁..."},{"pid":"2e2785e4b7e1f3a4980a0e7a1da234d41cc820b1","tid":1291808,"uid":140326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e220f11cf32db86f86dc7fd89222b175fb7bb154","tid":1291808,"uid":99402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"有number先得嫁..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"維持秩序果啲藍衫pc一定有，加上佢地無面具，大特寫拍佢一定有壓力"},{"pid":"b410325b62e6701d12fc72f0e4130d3e81eecb0a","tid":1291808,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"黑材料係共產中文，係痛腳"},{"pid":"c969453471811c4b585759902cc2aefb43b1b735","tid":1291808,"uid":205289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT